snippet.textDisplay: Kind of disappointed in Jimmy's monologue. He seems to run from the real topics. Sure it's depressing but it's your world we actually live in and he can turn around and make make light of the effortless role the politicians are making. no mentions of the Buffalo shooting, on mentions any other weekend events. If you want your ratings to go up you got to talk about real world issues man.
